    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Why does Zend_Uri_Http::setQuery() return the old query string?
I don't expect this behaviour and</p>

<p>Zend_Uri_Http::getQuery() does the same with the difference being that this method performs this check:</p>

<p>{{return strlen($this-&gt;_query) &gt; 0 ? $this-&gt;_query : false;}}</p>

<h2>To me this interface seems to be quite odd.</h2>

<p>{color:gray}
Note1: It seems like this oddity slipped in via <a href="http://framework.zend.com/issues/browse/ZF-351">http://framework.zend.com/issues/browse/ZF-351</a></p>

